 <purpose>
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the representation of the shape and the position of a product version used in another product version.
<example>This module might be used to represent the shape of a component in an assembly.</example>
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
      <li>replication of a geometric model through the application of a geometric transformation;</li>
      <li>import of the representation of the shape of an occurrence of a component in a representation of the shape of the product that uses it;</li>
      <li>items within the scope of application module <module_ref linkend="geometric_model_relationship:1_scope">Geometric model relationship</module_ref>, ISO/TS 10303-1403;</li>
      <li>items within the scope of application module <module_ref linkend="shape_property_assignment:1_scope">Shape property assignment</module_ref>, ISO/TS 10303-1032.</li>
   </inscope>

